      "text": "- 2025Q1 revenue baseline: East China 1.20M, North China 0.98M, South China 1.10M.\n- 2025Q2 revenue: East China 1.45M, North China 1.21M, South China 1.39M.\n- 2025Q3 revenue: East China 1.62M, North China 1.30M, South China 1.70M.\n- Gross margin improves from 0.39-0.42 in Q1 to 0.41-0.46 in Q3.\n- South China posts the strongest Q1-to-Q3 revenue growth, while East China remains the largest revenue base."
